title: KMFDM_Discography_1984-2014
description:
Kreated by rhob242

A tribute to KMFDM - 30 years of sucking, ripping the system, and kicking ass!

This should be the complete discography for the 30 years that has been KFMDM (Vinyls not included). All singles, EP's, Compilations, Live Albums, Remixes, LP's. 

The White Zombie remix album and Spider Man 2 Video Game OST are not included.

There are many redundant (duplicate or remixed) songs, but the discography is here on principle for the die-hard collector.

Extra Volumes 1-3 is pretty much all of the singles from the 90's with improved sound quality, so you could probably delete the singles if desired.

All of the 80's and 90's albums are the Wax Trax! recordings. The remastered recordings from Metropolis Records are a bit hard to come by.

Album artwork and CD artwork is included for each album.

All tags are setup for Windows Media Player, not tested with iTunes are anything else.

I had trouble compiling some of the songs with the correct length and sound quality for a couple early singles.

I did not include videos... anyone can rip from Youtube now days...

Apologies for any errors. Enjoy!
